- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is another possibility as the particles in programmable matter can be seen as agents that interact with each other.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with algorithms for programmable matter, which can be seen as a form of artificial intelligence.
